{
  "video_id": "CPVjktgYKo4",
  "title": "How Africa can keep rising | Ngozi Okonjo-Iweala",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12480.0,
      "end_time": 16335.0,
      "text": "The narrative of a rising Africa is being challenged."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16360.0,
      "end_time": 20816.0,
      "text": "About 10 years ago, I spoke about an Africa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20840.0,
      "end_time": 23536.0,
      "text": "an Africa of hope and opportunity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23560.0,
      "end_time": 25496.0,
      "text": "an Africa of entrepreneurs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25520.0,
      "end_time": 28976.0,
      "text": "an Africa very different from the Africa that you normally hear about"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 29000.0,
      "end_time": 31776.0,
      "text": "of death, poverty and disease."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 31800.0,
      "end_time": 33856.0,
      "text": "And that what I spoke about,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 33880.0,
      "end_time": 39336.0,
      "text": "became part of what is known now as the narrative of the rising Africa."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 39360.0,
      "end_time": 42696.0,
      "text": "I want to tell you two stories about this rising Africa."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 42720.0,
      "end_time": 44496.0,
      "text": "The first has to do with Rwanda,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 44520.0,
      "end_time": 47936.0,
      "text": "a country that has gone through many trials and tribulations."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 47960.0,
      "end_time": 52456.0,
      "text": "And Rwanda has decided to become the technology hub, or a technology hub"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 52480.0,
      "end_time": 53815.0,
      "text": "on the continent."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 53840.0,
      "end_time": 56856.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a country with mountainous and hilly terrain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 56880.0,
      "end_time": 58960.0,
      "text": "a little bit like here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 58120.0,
      "end_time": 61296.0,
      "text": "so it&#39;s very difficult to deliver services to people."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 61320.0,
      "end_time": 63160.0,
      "text": "So what has Rwanda said?"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 63400.0,
      "end_time": 66696.0,
      "text": "In order to save lives, it&#39;s going to try using drones"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 66720.0,
      "end_time": 69936.0,
      "text": "to deliver lifesaving drugs, vaccines and blood"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 69960.0,
      "end_time": 71976.0,
      "text": "to people in hard-to-reach places"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 72000.0,
      "end_time": 74496.0,
      "text": "in partnership with a company called Zipline,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 74520.0,
      "end_time": 79560.0,
      "text": "with UPS, and also with the Gavi, a global vaccine alliance."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 79800.0,
      "end_time": 81456.0,
      "text": "In doing this, it will save lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 81480.0,
      "end_time": 86776.0,
      "text": "This is part of the type of innovation we want to see in the rising Africa."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 86800.0,
      "end_time": 89336.0,
      "text": "The second story has to do with something"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 89360.0,
      "end_time": 92376.0,
      "text": "that I&#39;m sure most of you have seen or will remember."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 92400.0,
      "end_time": 96296.0,
      "text": "Very often, countries in Africa suffer drought and floods,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 96320.0,
      "end_time": 100150.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s getting more frequent because of climate change effects."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 100400.0,
      "end_time": 105736.0,
      "text": "When this happens, they normally wait for international appeals to raise money."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 105760.0,
      "end_time": 109136.0,
      "text": "You see pictures of children with flies on their faces,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 109160.0,
      "end_time": 111655.0,
      "text": "carcasses of dead animals and so on."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 111680.0,
      "end_time": 114696.0,
      "text": "Now these countries, 32 countries, came together"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 114720.0,
      "end_time": 117176.0,
      "text": "under the auspices of the African Union"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 117200.0,
      "end_time": 122216.0,
      "text": "and decided to form an organization called the African Risk Capacity."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 122240.0,
      "end_time": 123455.0,
      "text": "What does it do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 123480.0,
      "end_time": 125576.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a weather-based insurance agency,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 125600.0,
      "end_time": 129976.0,
      "text": "and what these countries do is to pay insurance each year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 130000.0,
      "end_time": 132936.0,
      "text": "about 3 million dollars a year of their own resources,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 132960.0,
      "end_time": 137776.0,
      "text": "so that in the event they have a difficult drought situation or flood,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 137800.0,
      "end_time": 140416.0,
      "text": "this money will be paid out to them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 140440.0,
      "end_time": 143176.0,
      "text": "which they can then use to take care of their populations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 143200.0,
      "end_time": 145976.0,
      "text": "instead of waiting for aid to come."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 146000.0,
      "end_time": 150216.0,
      "text": "The African Risk Capacity last year paid 26 million dollars"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 150240.0,
      "end_time": 152736.0,
      "text": "to Mauritania, Senegal and Niger."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 152760.0,
      "end_time": 158215.0,
      "text": "This enabled them to take care of 1.3 million people affected by drought."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 158240.0,
      "end_time": 160576.0,
      "text": "They were able to restore livelihoods,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 160600.0,
      "end_time": 163296.0,
      "text": "buy fodder for cattle, feed children in school"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 163320.0,
      "end_time": 169960.0,
      "text": "and in short keep the populations home instead of migrating out of the area."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 169120.0,
      "end_time": 170976.0,
      "text": "So these are the kinds of stories"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 171000.0,
      "end_time": 174616.0,
      "text": "of an Africa ready to take responsibility for itself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 174640.0,
      "end_time": 177815.0,
      "text": "and to look for solutions for its own problems."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 177840.0,
      "end_time": 180336.0,
      "text": "But that narrative is being challenged now"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 180360.0,
      "end_time": 185176.0,
      "text": "because the continent has not been doing well in the last two years."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 185200.0,
      "end_time": 188136.0,
      "text": "It had been growing at five percent per annum"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 188160.0,
      "end_time": 190960.0,
      "text": "for the last one and a half decades,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 190120.0,
      "end_time": 192896.0,
      "text": "but this year&#39;s forecast was three percent. Why?"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 192920.0,
      "end_time": 197950.0,
      "text": "In an uncertain global environment, commodity prices have fallen."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 197120.0,
      "end_time": 200296.0,
      "text": "Many of the economies are still commodity driven,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 200320.0,
      "end_time": 202880.0,
      "text": "and therefore their performance has slipped."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 203480.0,
      "end_time": 207456.0,
      "text": "And now the issue of Brexit doesn&#39;t make it any easier."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 207480.0,
      "end_time": 211960.0,
      "text": "I never knew that the Brexit could happen"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 211120.0,
      "end_time": 215256.0,
      "text": "and that it could be one of the things that would cause global uncertainty"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 215280.0,
      "end_time": 216576.0,
      "text": "such as we have."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 216600.0,
      "end_time": 218775.0,
      "text": "So now we&#39;ve got this situation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 218800.0,
      "end_time": 221656.0,
      "text": "and I think it&#39;s time to take stock"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 221680.0,
      "end_time": 226536.0,
      "text": "and to say what were the things that the African countries did right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 226560.0,
      "end_time": 228200.0,
      "text": "What did they do wrong?"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 228840.0,
      "end_time": 231296.0,
      "text": "How do we build on all of this and learn lessons"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 231320.0,
      "end_time": 234120.0,
      "text": "so that we can keep Africa rising?"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 234720.0,
      "end_time": 238800.0,
      "text": "So let me talk about six things that I think we did right."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 238720.0,
      "end_time": 242160.0,
      "text": "The first is managing our economies better."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 242400.0,
      "end_time": 246296.0,
      "text": "The &#39;80s and &#39;90s were the lost decades, when Africa was not doing well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 246320.0,
      "end_time": 249936.0,
      "text": "and some of you will remember an \"Economist\" cover"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 249960.0,
      "end_time": 251976.0,
      "text": "that said, \"The Lost Continent.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 252000.0,
      "end_time": 256960.0,
      "text": "But in the 2000s, policymakers learned"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 256120.0,
      "end_time": 260375.0,
      "text": "that they needed to manage the macroeconomic environment better,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 260399.0,
      "end_time": 261935.0,
      "text": "to ensure stability,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 261959.0,
      "end_time": 264575.0,
      "text": "keep inflation low in single digits,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 264600.0,
      "end_time": 270176.0,
      "text": "keep their fiscal deficits low, below three percent of GDP,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 270200.0,
      "end_time": 274960.0,
      "text": "give investors, both domestic and foreign,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 274120.0,
      "end_time": 277936.0,
      "text": "some stability so they&#39;ll have confidence to invest in these economies."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 277960.0,
      "end_time": 279455.0,
      "text": "So that was number one."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 279480.0,
      "end_time": 280816.0,
      "text": "Two, debt."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 280840.0,
      "end_time": 286536.0,
      "text": "In 1994, the debt-to-GDP ratio of African countries was 130 percent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 286560.0,
      "end_time": 288816.0,
      "text": "and they didn&#39;t have fiscal space."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 288840.0,
      "end_time": 291856.0,
      "text": "They couldn&#39;t use their resources to invest in their development"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 291880.0,
      "end_time": 293336.0,
      "text": "because they were paying debt."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 293360.0,
      "end_time": 298960.0,
      "text": "There may be some of you in this room who worked to support African countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 298120.0,
      "end_time": 299416.0,
      "text": "to get debt relief."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 299440.0,
      "end_time": 303896.0,
      "text": "So private creditors, multilaterals and bilaterals came together"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 303920.0,
      "end_time": 307536.0,
      "text": "and decided to do the Highly Indebted Poor Countries Initiative"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 307560.0,
      "end_time": 308816.0,
      "text": "and give debt relief."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 308840.0,
      "end_time": 310936.0,
      "text": "So this debt relief in 2005"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 310960.0,
      "end_time": 314895.0,
      "text": "made the debt-to-GDP ratio fall down to about 30 percent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 314920.0,
      "end_time": 318816.0,
      "text": "and there was enough resources to try and reinvest."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 318840.0,
      "end_time": 321296.0,
      "text": "The third thing was loss-making enterprises."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 321320.0,
      "end_time": 323376.0,
      "text": "Governments were involved in business"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 323400.0,
      "end_time": 325655.0,
      "text": "which they had no business being in."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 325680.0,
      "end_time": 328776.0,
      "text": "And they were running businesses, they were making losses."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 328800.0,
      "end_time": 331536.0,
      "text": "So some of these enterprises were restructured,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 331560.0,
      "end_time": 333976.0,
      "text": "commercialized, privatized or closed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 334000.0,
      "end_time": 337200.0,
      "text": "and they became less of a burden on government."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 338800.0,
      "end_time": 340479.0,
      "text": "The fourth thing was a very interesting thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 341200.0,
      "end_time": 343496.0,
      "text": "The telecoms revolution came,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 343520.0,
      "end_time": 346960.0,
      "text": "and African countries jumped on it."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 346120.0,
      "end_time": 348736.0,
      "text": "In 2000, we had 11 million phone lines."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 348760.0,
      "end_time": 354960.0,
      "text": "Today, we have about 687 million mobile lines on the continent."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 354120.0,
      "end_time": 355936.0,
      "text": "And this has enabled us"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 355960.0,
      "end_time": 358616.0,
      "text": "to go, move forward with some mobile technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 358640.0,
      "end_time": 361256.0,
      "text": "where Africa is actually leading."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 361280.0,
      "end_time": 363816.0,
      "text": "In Kenya, the development of mobile money --"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 363840.0,
      "end_time": 366616.0,
      "text": "M-Pesa, which all of you have heard about --"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 366640.0,
      "end_time": 370960.0,
      "text": "it took some time for the world to notice that Africa was ahead"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 370120.0,
      "end_time": 371656.0,
      "text": "in this particular technology."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 371680.0,
      "end_time": 374896.0,
      "text": "And this mobile money is also providing a platform"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 374920.0,
      "end_time": 377376.0,
      "text": "for access to alternative energy."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 377400.0,
      "end_time": 380895.0,
      "text": "You know, people who can now pay for solar"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 380920.0,
      "end_time": 385136.0,
      "text": "the same way they pay for cards for their telephone."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 385160.0,
      "end_time": 389680.0,
      "text": "So this was a very good development, something that went right."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 390240.0,
      "end_time": 394736.0,
      "text": "We also invested more in education and health, not enough,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 394760.0,
      "end_time": 396416.0,
      "text": "but there were some improvements."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 396440.0,
      "end_time": 401960.0,
      "text": "250 million children were immunized in the last one and a half decades."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 402520.0,
      "end_time": 405895.0,
      "text": "The other thing was that conflicts decreased."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 405920.0,
      "end_time": 407976.0,
      "text": "There were many conflicts on the continent."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 408000.0,
      "end_time": 409456.0,
      "text": "Many of you are aware of that."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 409480.0,
      "end_time": 414296.0,
      "text": "But they came down, and our leaders even managed to dampen some coups."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 414320.0,
      "end_time": 418376.0,
      "text": "New types of conflicts have emerged, and I&#39;ll refer to those later."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 418400.0,
      "end_time": 422150.0,
      "text": "So based on all this, there&#39;s also some differentiation on the continent"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 422400.0,
      "end_time": 423496.0,
      "text": "that I want you to know about,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 423520.0,
      "end_time": 426150.0,
      "text": "because even as the doom and gloom is here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 426400.0,
      "end_time": 430160.0,
      "text": "there are some countries -- Côte d&#39;Ivoire, Kenya, Ethiopia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 430400.0,
      "end_time": 434320.0,
      "text": "Tanzania and Senegal are performing relatively well at the moment."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 435120.0,
      "end_time": 437256.0,
      "text": "But what did we do wrong?"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 437280.0,
      "end_time": 438655.0,
      "text": "Let me mention eight things."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 438680.0,
      "end_time": 440856.0,
      "text": "You have to have more things wrong than right."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 440880.0,
      "end_time": 442336.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 442360.0,
      "end_time": 444736.0,
      "text": "So there are eight things we did wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 444760.0,
      "end_time": 448280.0,
      "text": "The first was that even though we grew, we didn&#39;t create enough jobs."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 448800.0,
      "end_time": 450696.0,
      "text": "We didn&#39;t create jobs for our youth."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 450720.0,
      "end_time": 453656.0,
      "text": "Youth unemployment on the continent is about 15 percent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 453680.0,
      "end_time": 456720.0,
      "text": "and underemployment is a serious problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 457400.0,
      "end_time": 462936.0,
      "text": "The second thing that we did is that the quality of growth was not good enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 462960.0,
      "end_time": 466496.0,
      "text": "Even those jobs we created were low-productivity jobs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 466520.0,
      "end_time": 470150.0,
      "text": "so we moved people from low-productivity agriculture"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 470400.0,
      "end_time": 473976.0,
      "text": "to low-productivity commerce and working in the informal sector"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 474000.0,
      "end_time": 475720.0,
      "text": "in the urban areas."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 476240.0,
      "end_time": 480400.0,
      "text": "The third thing is that inequality increased."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 480600.0,
      "end_time": 485576.0,
      "text": "So we created more billionaires."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 485600.0,
      "end_time": 488296.0,
      "text": "50 billionaires worth 96 billion dollars"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 488320.0,
      "end_time": 493159.0,
      "text": "own more wealth than the bottom 75 million people on the continent."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 493920.0,
      "end_time": 495496.0,
      "text": "Poverty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 495520.0,
      "end_time": 499895.0,
      "text": "the proportion of people in poverty -- that&#39;s the fourth thing -- did decrease,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 499920.0,
      "end_time": 504160.0,
      "text": "but the absolute numbers did not because of population growth."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 504400.0,
      "end_time": 506616.0,
      "text": "And population growth is something"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 506640.0,
      "end_time": 510560.0,
      "text": "that we don&#39;t have enough of a dialogue about on the continent."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 510800.0,
      "end_time": 513216.0,
      "text": "And I think we will need to get a handle on it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 513240.0,
      "end_time": 516496.0,
      "text": "particularly how we educate girls."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 516520.0,
      "end_time": 521159.0,
      "text": "That is the road to really working on this particular issue."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 521880.0,
      "end_time": 528696.0,
      "text": "The fifth thing is that we didn&#39;t invest enough in infrastructure."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 528720.0,
      "end_time": 530816.0,
      "text": "We had investment from the Chinese."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 530840.0,
      "end_time": 534560.0,
      "text": "That helped some countries, but it&#39;s not enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 534800.0,
      "end_time": 537416.0,
      "text": "The consumption of electricity in Africa on the continent"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 537440.0,
      "end_time": 541160.0,
      "text": "in Sub-Saharan Africa is equivalent to Spain."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 541400.0,
      "end_time": 544496.0,
      "text": "The total consumption is equivalent to that of Spain."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 544520.0,
      "end_time": 547175.0,
      "text": "So many people are living in the dark,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 547200.0,
      "end_time": 550776.0,
      "text": "and as the President of the African Development Bank said recently,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 550800.0,
      "end_time": 553790.0,
      "text": "Africa cannot develop in the dark."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 554120.0,
      "end_time": 556256.0,
      "text": "The other thing we have not done"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 556280.0,
      "end_time": 561696.0,
      "text": "is that our economies retain the same structure"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 561720.0,
      "end_time": 563336.0,
      "text": "that we&#39;ve had for decades."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 563360.0,
      "end_time": 565160.0,
      "text": "So even though we&#39;ve been growing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 565400.0,
      "end_time": 567736.0,
      "text": "the structure of the economies has not changed very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 567760.0,
      "end_time": 570336.0,
      "text": "We are still exporting commodities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 570360.0,
      "end_time": 574216.0,
      "text": "and exporting commodities is what? It&#39;s exporting jobs."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 574240.0,
      "end_time": 577536.0,
      "text": "Our manufacturing value-added is only 11 percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 577560.0,
      "end_time": 582950.0,
      "text": "We are not creating enough decent manufacturing jobs for our youth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 582120.0,
      "end_time": 584736.0,
      "text": "and trade among ourselves is low."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 584760.0,
      "end_time": 588256.0,
      "text": "Only about 12 percent of our trade is among ourselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 588280.0,
      "end_time": 590976.0,
      "text": "So that&#39;s another serious problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 591000.0,
      "end_time": 593960.0,
      "text": "Then governance."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 593120.0,
      "end_time": 595536.0,
      "text": "Governance is a serious issue."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 595560.0,
      "end_time": 597776.0,
      "text": "We have weak institutions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 597800.0,
      "end_time": 602815.0,
      "text": "and sometimes nonexistent institutions, and I think this gives way for corruption."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 602840.0,
      "end_time": 608560.0,
      "text": "Corruption is an issue that we have not yet gotten a good enough handle on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 608800.0,
      "end_time": 610696.0,
      "text": "and we have to fight tooth and nail,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 610720.0,
      "end_time": 614296.0,
      "text": "that and increased transparency in the way we manage our economies"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 614320.0,
      "end_time": 616776.0,
      "text": "and the way we manage our finances."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 616800.0,
      "end_time": 621536.0,
      "text": "We also need to be wary of new conflicts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 621560.0,
      "end_time": 623496.0,
      "text": "new types of conflicts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 623520.0,
      "end_time": 626736.0,
      "text": "such as we have with Boko Haram in my country, Nigeria,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 626760.0,
      "end_time": 628816.0,
      "text": "and with Al-Shabaab in Kenya."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 628840.0,
      "end_time": 632176.0,
      "text": "We need to partner with international partners,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 632200.0,
      "end_time": 635560.0,
      "text": "developed countries, to fight this together."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 635800.0,
      "end_time": 636976.0,
      "text": "Otherwise, we create a new reality"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 637000.0,
      "end_time": 640256.0,
      "text": "which is not the type we want for a rising Africa."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 640280.0,
      "end_time": 643815.0,
      "text": "And finally, the issue of education."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 643840.0,
      "end_time": 647136.0,
      "text": "Our education systems in many countries are broken."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 647160.0,
      "end_time": 651695.0,
      "text": "We are not creating the types of skills needed for the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 651720.0,
      "end_time": 654360.0,
      "text": "So we have to find a way to educate better."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 654920.0,
      "end_time": 657640.0,
      "text": "So those are the things that we are not doing right."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 658240.0,
      "end_time": 660640.0,
      "text": "Now, where do we go from there?"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 661240.0,
      "end_time": 665936.0,
      "text": "I believe that the way forward is to learn to manage success."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 665960.0,
      "end_time": 669696.0,
      "text": "Very often, when people succeed or countries succeed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 669720.0,
      "end_time": 671920.0,
      "text": "they forget what made them succeed."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 672680.0,
      "end_time": 675215.0,
      "text": "Learning what you&#39;re successful at,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 675240.0,
      "end_time": 677656.0,
      "text": "managing it and keeping it is vital for us."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 677680.0,
      "end_time": 679896.0,
      "text": "So all those things I said we did right,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 679920.0,
      "end_time": 683815.0,
      "text": "we have to learn to do it right again, keep doing it right."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 683840.0,
      "end_time": 687416.0,
      "text": "Managing the economy while creating stability is vital,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 687440.0,
      "end_time": 690936.0,
      "text": "getting prices right, and policy consistency."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 690960.0,
      "end_time": 693336.0,
      "text": "Very often, we are not consistent."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 693360.0,
      "end_time": 695616.0,
      "text": "One regime goes out, another comes in"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 695640.0,
      "end_time": 699960.0,
      "text": "and they throw away even the functioning policies that were there before."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 699120.0,
      "end_time": 700376.0,
      "text": "What does this do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 700400.0,
      "end_time": 702776.0,
      "text": "It creates uncertainty for people, for households,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 702800.0,
      "end_time": 704175.0,
      "text": "uncertainties for business."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 704200.0,
      "end_time": 706896.0,
      "text": "They don&#39;t know whether and how to invest."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 706920.0,
      "end_time": 711256.0,
      "text": "Debt: we must manage the success we had in reducing our debt,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 711280.0,
      "end_time": 713815.0,
      "text": "but now countries are back to borrowing again,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 713840.0,
      "end_time": 717256.0,
      "text": "and we see our debt-to-GDP ratio beginning to creep up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 717280.0,
      "end_time": 718736.0,
      "text": "and in certain countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 718760.0,
      "end_time": 721256.0,
      "text": "debt is becoming a problem, so we have to avoid that."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 721280.0,
      "end_time": 722736.0,
      "text": "So managing success."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 722760.0,
      "end_time": 725415.0,
      "text": "The next thing is focusing with a laser beam"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 725440.0,
      "end_time": 727296.0,
      "text": "on those things we did not do well."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 727320.0,
      "end_time": 729176.0,
      "text": "First and foremost is infrastructure."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 729200.0,
      "end_time": 732776.0,
      "text": "Yes, most countries now recognize they have to invest in this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 732800.0,
      "end_time": 735415.0,
      "text": "and they are trying to do the best they can to do that."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 735440.0,
      "end_time": 736656.0,
      "text": "We must."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 736680.0,
      "end_time": 738335.0,
      "text": "The most important thing is power."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 738360.0,
      "end_time": 740616.0,
      "text": "You cannot develop in the dark."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 740640.0,
      "end_time": 742896.0,
      "text": "And then governance and corruption:"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 742920.0,
      "end_time": 744136.0,
      "text": "we have to fight."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 744160.0,
      "end_time": 746935.0,
      "text": "We have to make our countries transparent."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 746960.0,
      "end_time": 750536.0,
      "text": "And above all, we have to engage our young people."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 750560.0,
      "end_time": 752776.0,
      "text": "We have genius in our young people."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 752800.0,
      "end_time": 754550.0,
      "text": "I see it every day."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 754800.0,
      "end_time": 757616.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s what makes me wake up in the morning and feel ready to go."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 757640.0,
      "end_time": 760160.0,
      "text": "We have to unleash the genius of our young people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 760400.0,
      "end_time": 763295.0,
      "text": "get out of their way, support them to create and innovate"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 763320.0,
      "end_time": 764536.0,
      "text": "and lead the way."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 764560.0,
      "end_time": 767256.0,
      "text": "And I know that they will lead us in the right direction."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 767280.0,
      "end_time": 769456.0,
      "text": "And our women, and our girls:"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 769480.0,
      "end_time": 772536.0,
      "text": "we have to recognize that girls and women are a gift."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 772560.0,
      "end_time": 774550.0,
      "text": "They have strength,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 774800.0,
      "end_time": 776216.0,
      "text": "and we have to unleash that strength"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 776240.0,
      "end_time": 779176.0,
      "text": "so that they can contribute to the continent."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 779200.0,
      "end_time": 783160.0,
      "text": "I strongly believe that when we do all of these things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 783400.0,
      "end_time": 786256.0,
      "text": "we find that the rising Africa narrative"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 786280.0,
      "end_time": 787856.0,
      "text": "is not a fluke."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 787880.0,
      "end_time": 789120.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a trend."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 789720.0,
      "end_time": 793536.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a trend, and if we continue, if we unleash our youth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 793560.0,
      "end_time": 794896.0,
      "text": "if we unleash our women,"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 794920.0,
      "end_time": 796935.0,
      "text": "we may step backwards sometimes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 796960.0,
      "end_time": 798856.0,
      "text": "we may even step sideways,"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 798880.0,
      "end_time": 800496.0,
      "text": "but the trend is clear."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 800520.0,
      "end_time": 802536.0,
      "text": "Africa will continue to rise."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 802560.0,
      "end_time": 806295.0,
      "text": "And I tell you businesspeople in the audience,"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 806320.0,
      "end_time": 809776.0,
      "text": "investment in Africa is not for today, is not for tomorrow,"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 809800.0,
      "end_time": 813550.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s not a short-term thing, it&#39;s a longer term thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 813800.0,
      "end_time": 815496.0,
      "text": "But if you are not invested in Africa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 815520.0,
      "end_time": 816936.0,
      "text": "then you will be missing"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 816960.0,
      "end_time": 821216.0,
      "text": "one of the most important emerging opportunities in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 821240.0,
      "end_time": 822456.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 822480.0,
      "end_time": 825000.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 831227.0,
      "end_time": 833896.0,
      "text": "Kelly Stoetzel: So you mentioned corruption in your talk,"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 833920.0,
      "end_time": 837415.0,
      "text": "and you&#39;re known, well-known as a strong anticorruption fighter."
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 837440.0,
      "end_time": 839976.0,
      "text": "But that&#39;s had consequences."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 840000.0,
      "end_time": 842936.0,
      "text": "People have fought back, and your mother was kidnapped."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 842960.0,
      "end_time": 844520.0,
      "text": "How have you been handling this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 845280.0,
      "end_time": 847456.0,
      "text": "Ngozi Okonjo-Iweala: It&#39;s been very difficult."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 847480.0,
      "end_time": 851816.0,
      "text": "Thank you for mentioning the issue of the kidnap of my mother."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 851840.0,
      "end_time": 854416.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a very difficult subject."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 854440.0,
      "end_time": 858296.0,
      "text": "But what it means is that when you fight corruption,"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 858320.0,
      "end_time": 861736.0,
      "text": "when you touch the pockets of people who are stealing money,"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 861760.0,
      "end_time": 863616.0,
      "text": "they don&#39;t just keep quiet."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 863640.0,
      "end_time": 867295.0,
      "text": "They fight back, and the issue for you is when they try to intimidate you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 867320.0,
      "end_time": 870776.0,
      "text": "do you give up, or do you fight on?"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 870800.0,
      "end_time": 873935.0,
      "text": "Do you find a way to stay on and fight back?"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 873960.0,
      "end_time": 878216.0,
      "text": "And the answer that I had with the teams I worked with"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 878240.0,
      "end_time": 880160.0,
      "text": "is we have to fight on."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 880400.0,
      "end_time": 881856.0,
      "text": "We have to create those institutions."
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 881880.0,
      "end_time": 885960.0,
      "text": "We have to find ways to stop these people"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 885120.0,
      "end_time": 888296.0,
      "text": "from taking away the heritage of the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 888320.0,
      "end_time": 890216.0,
      "text": "And so that&#39;s what we did."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 890240.0,
      "end_time": 893856.0,
      "text": "And even out of government, we continued to make that point."
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 893880.0,
      "end_time": 897856.0,
      "text": "In our countries, nobody, nobody is going to fight corruption"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 897880.0,
      "end_time": 899415.0,
      "text": "for us but us."
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 899440.0,
      "end_time": 901656.0,
      "text": "And therefore, that comes with consequences,"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 901680.0,
      "end_time": 903575.0,
      "text": "and we just have to do the best we can."
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 903600.0,
      "end_time": 907160.0,
      "text": "But I thank you and thank TED for giving us a voice"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 907400.0,
      "end_time": 910336.0,
      "text": "to say to those people, you will not win,"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 910360.0,
      "end_time": 912696.0,
      "text": "and we will not be intimidated."
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 912720.0,
      "end_time": 913936.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 913960.0,
      "end_time": 915176.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 915200.0,
      "end_time": 918666.0,
      "text": "Kelly Stoetzel: Thank you so much for your great talk and important work."
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 918690.0,
      "end_time": 922600.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}